TRIBUTE PAGE With basic knowledge of HTML and CSS, you can create a webpage dedicated to someone you admire. Write about their admirable qualities, add images, and design a visually appealing layout.
Experiment with font styles, use paragraphs effectively, and play with background colors. 
This project allows you to express your admiration in a simple and personalized way.


